    "SCI": "State Commitment Index. Federal budget activity + state-linked contractor starts + 2% mortgage volume as state expenditure.",
    "track_a": "Private market signal. Non-state developer entry + cash DKP transactions (non-mortgage) + asking price momentum. Mariupol penalised: Bellingcat/Shumanov confirm near-zero genuine private entry.",
    "track_b": "Residential outcome signal. Secondary listing depth (Domclick counts) + buyer permanence score (PSB/VTB disclosures) + rental-to-purchase ratio (estimated where marked).",
    "composite": "SCI × 0.4 + Track A × 0.6. Weighted blend of state commitment and private market signal.",
    "spread": "Track B minus Composite (SCI×0.4 + A×0.6). Positive = residential confidence LEADS state+private composite. Negative = composite OUTPACES residential reality — the fragility signal.",
